10
00:00:27,140 --> 00:00:29,620
Priprav sa a počkaj si na to.

11
00:00:36,620 --> 00:00:38,130
Pusti ma!

12
00:00:39,680 --> 00:00:41,640
Nič ťa do toho nie je. 
Vyriešim si to sama.

13
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:44,690
Prepáč, Gyu Min.

14
00:00:44,690 --> 00:00:47,090
Musela som sa zblázniť, keď som im verila.

15
00:00:47,090 --> 00:00:48,780
Poďme domov.

16
00:00:49,830 --> 00:00:51,580
Lee Roo Mi.

17
00:00:51,960 --> 00:00:53,480
Preber sa.

18
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:55,920
